作为美国联邦快速铁路网络的一部分，“狼獾号列车”亦随之升级为准高速旅客列车。<ref name="hsrstrategicplanpr">{{cite web|url=http://www.fra.dot.gov/Downloads/RRdev/hsrpressrelease.pdf |format=PDF |title=High-Speed Rail Strategic Plan: Press Release & Highlights |publisher= 美国交通部 |date=2009年4月16日 |accessdate=2009-04-20 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090422185751/http://www.fra.dot.gov/Downloads/RRdev/hsrpressrelease.pdf |archivedate=April 22, 2009 }}</ref> 2006年，[[聯邦鐵路管理局|美国聯邦鐵路管理局]]计划将[[底特律|底特律]]↔[[芝加哥|芝加哥]]间的铁路升级为快速铁路。<ref name="MICHIGAN06">{{cite web | url = http://www.amtrak.com/pdf/factsheets/MICHIGAN06.pdf | title = Amtrak Fact Sheet, Fiscal Year 2006 | work = State of Michigan | accessdate = 2007-05-13 | archive-date = 2007-09-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070925223635/http://www.amtrak.com/pdf/factsheets/MICHIGAN06.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref> 2010年10月，[[密歇根州|密歇根州]]收到来自美国联邦政府1.5亿美元资金，用于将[[卡拉马祖_(密歇根州)|卡拉马祖]]↔[[迪尔伯恩|迪尔伯恩]]间的铁路提速至110英里/小时（180千米/小时）。<ref>{{cite web|title=Michigan awarded $150M for high-speed rail route［密歇根州獲得1.5亿美元铁路提速经费］|url=http://www.detnews.com/article/20101025/METRO05/10250393/Michigan-awarded-$150M-for-high-speed-rail-route.|accessdate=2010年10月28日|author=|date=2010年10月25日|format=|publisher=底特律新闻报|language=en}}{{dead link|date=May 2013}}</ref> 截至2016年，位于[[密歇根州|密歇根州]]的[[巴特尔克里克_(密歇根州)|战斗溪]]↔[[杰克逊_(密歇根州)|杰克逊]]区段已完成提速改造，此次工程共更换26000根枕木、维修及安装15处道岔、对29处弯道进行截弯取直、改善23处平交道口。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.mlive.com/news/ann-arbor/index.ssf/2017/01/train_ridership_projections_pe.html|title=Train ridership projections 'perhaps not well founded,' city official says|newspaper=MLive.com|language=en-US|access-date=2017-01-31|archive-date=2018-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180202012542/http://www.mlive.com/news/ann-arbor/index.ssf/2017/01/train_ridership_projections_pe.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

“狼獾号列车”所使用的铁路线路中的[[印第安纳州|印第安纳州]]波特（Porter）↔[[密歇根州|密歇根州]][[卡拉马祖_(密歇根州)|卡拉马祖]]区段长{{convert|97|mi|km|adj=on}}的铁路线路为[[美铁|美铁]]自有，其为[[美铁|美铁]]除[[东北走廊|东北走廊]]外最长的自有铁路线路。<ref name="MICHIGAN06" /> 2002年1月起，[[美铁|美铁]]开始开展将这段自有铁路提速至110英里/小时（180千米/小时）的工程。<ref>Amtrak Press Release, February 15, 2012, AMTRAK 110 MPH MICHIGAN SERVICE CELEBRATION,"Amtrak extended ITCS coverage to the western and eastern ends of the line between Porter and Kalamazoo last year, completing the system across 97 miles of track and permitting the higher speeds on about 80 miles of the route, 64 miles in Michigan and 16 in Indiana. The FRA granted approval for regular service at 110 mph (177 km/h) on Jan. 27, 2012."</ref> 

2012年12月，密歇根州交通部完成了购买[[诺福克南方铁路公司|诺福克南方铁路公司]]所属的[[卡拉马祖_(密歇根州)|卡拉马祖]]↔[[迪尔伯恩|迪尔伯恩]]的长{{convert|135|mi|km}}铁路的相关程序。<ref name="2015Equire110mph">{{cite news|last1=Bowman|first1=Jennifer|title=Track fixes to allow 110-mph Amtrak travel through B.C.|url=http://www.battlecreekenquirer.com/story/news/local/2015/07/29/track-fixes-allow-mph-amtrak-travel-bc/30842183/|accessdate=22 April 2016|work=Battle Creek Enquirer|date=29 July 2015}}</ref> 这使得美国政府出面维护并升级这段铁路变得更加容易，为2017年底将这段铁路提速至{{convert|110|mph|km/h|adj=on}}创造的有利条件。密歇根州交通部同时批准了[[伊普西蘭蒂_(密歇根州)|伊普西蘭蒂]]以东的铁路线路复线化工程。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.michigan.gov/mdot/0%2c4616%2c7-151-9620_11057-263585--%2c00.html |title=MDOT - MDOT seeks to improve both passenger and freight rail lines with purchase of Norfolk Southern Railway track<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2020-07-20 |archive-date=2013-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131213092222/http://www.michigan.gov/mdot/0%2c4616%2c7-151-9620_11057-263585--%2c00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2019年8月，美铁开始考虑将西端终点由[[芝加哥|芝加哥]]延至[[多伦多|多伦多]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=Amtrak considers extending Wolverine line from Chicago to Toronto［美铁计划将狼獾号列车的终点由芝加哥延至多伦多］|url=https://www.woodtv.com/news/national/amtrak-considers-proposal-to-extend-rail-service-from-chicago-to-toronto/?platform=hootsuite|accessdate=2019-08-13|author=|date=2019-08-09|last=NBC staff|format=|publisher=|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108015724/https://www.woodtv.com/news/national/amtrak-considers-proposal-to-extend-rail-service-from-chicago-to-toronto/?platform=hootsuite|dead-url=no}}</ref>

